  "excerpt": "Kicking off 2017 with my newest collection with American Crafts , On A Whim! It was definitely inspired by the optimistic and confident girls and women out their doing fun things and seeking bright and bold adventures. I can't wait…",
  "legacyPath": "/blog/2017/1/2/new-collection-on-a-whim",
  "legacyFile": "blog__2017__1__2__new-collection-on-a-whim.html",
  "imageCount": 5,
  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595837622562-IP7GQAOOQT6P945PMJJK/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Kicking off 2017 with my newest collection with <a href=\"http://americancrafts.typepad.com/studio/\">American Crafts</a>, On A Whim! It was definitely inspired by the optimistic and confident girls and women out their doing fun things and seeking bright and bold adventures. I can't wait to see how you document your life with this mix of color and whimsy.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595837655446-2JNK1Y3W9QKGJHW8Q8QY/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Capture spontaneity and fun times with On a Whim. Bold graphics and cool patterns complement fun phrases in a host of bright colors. Pineapple yellow, flamingo pink and ocean blue coordinate with accents of gold, green, and red. Document your favorite adventures with the cute icons of On a Whim!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"1c-_AC_AT_OnAWhim_CreativeSamples-4.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595837685670-BG35F8A9YMSBSS4NRUYJ/1c-_AC_AT_OnAWhim_CreativeSamples-4.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"1d-AT_OnAWhim_Blog_Images-01.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595837698987-08TNBH1P9FZXU8ZK2QF0/1d-AT_OnAWhim_Blog_Images-01.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"1e-AT_OnAWhim_Blog_Images-02.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595837696437-IIRCSQKSXPFX07GCZ5D1/1e-AT_OnAWhim_Blog_Images-02.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Let us know what your favorites are in the comments! I'll be at <a href=\"http://www.creativationshow.org/\">Creativation</a> (formerly CHA) in a couple weeks in Phoenix, AZ and I'll be sure to capture and share it with you here and on my <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/amytangerine1\">YouTube channel</a>.</p>"
}